						<summary>

						<p>This seems to record a gift for a lamp in the temple by one Amalan Ayyāṟaṉ the headman of Iṟaiyāṉkuḍi in••••ṅgala-kūṟṟam, and also some provision made for the sacred bath (and offerings ?) of the deity on the day of Tiruvādirai (Ārdrā) in Mārgaḻi month.</p>						

						</summary>
